2025-11-14 23:50:00 | INFO     | kempian.app          | All resume data: {'full_name': 'VINIT PATIL', 'email': 'vinitpatil4958@gmail.com', 'phone': None, 'location': 'Shivaji Nagar Pune', 'experience_years': 4, 'education': "Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science at S.S.V.P.S College of Engineering, 2020 – 2024", 'work_experience': ', build practical experience, and grow as part of', 'projects': "Shoe Store Application: Designed a seamless shopping experience with React.js for intuitive navigation. Built a Node.js and Express.js backend to fetch the products data and image. Instagram Clone: Simplified clone of Instagram's homepage focusing on replicating the core layout and design elements. FaceBook Clone: Replicated Instagram's core homepage layout and features for a visually appealing UI. Adidas Homepage Clone: Developed a pixel-perfect replica of Adidas India's homepage for design practice. Zomato Clone: Built a visually accurate clone of Zomato India's homepage with a focus on UI/UX.", 'certifications': 'Zomato Clone: React.js (Basic) - HackerRank, Node.js (Basic) - HackerRank, JavaScript (Basic) - HackerRank', 'summary': 'Aspiring web developer with a strong passion for creating visually appealing and user-friendly websites. Proficient in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, with a solid understanding of responsive design principles and modern web development practices. Skilled at learning quickly, solving problems, and adapting to new tools and technologies. Eager to contribute to real-world projects, build practical experience, and grow as part of a dynamic development team.', 'skills': ['Teamwork', 'Javascript', 'CSS', 'Express', 'Html', 'React', 'Express.js', 'Responsive Design', 'Github', 'SQL', 'JavaScript', 'Node.js', 'Css', 'React.js', 'HTML', 'Mongodb', 'Git', 'Sql', 'MongoDB', 'Node.Js', 'Postman'], 'raw_text': "vinitpatil4958@gmail.com\nVINIT PATIL\nShivaji Nagar Pune\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/-vinit-patil/\nWeb-Developer\nhttps://github.com/\nSUMMARY\nAspiring web developer with a strong passion for creating visually appealing and user-friendly websites.\nProficient in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, with a solid understanding of responsive design principles and\nmodern web development practices. Skilled at learning quickly, solving problems, and adapting to new tools\nand technologies. Eager to contribute to real-world projects, build practical experience, and grow as part of\na dynamic development team.\nEDUCATION PROJECT’S\nBachelor's Degree in Computer Science\nShoe Store Application\nS.S.V.P.S College of Engineering Designed a seamless shopping experience with React.js for\n2020 – 2024 intuitive navigation\nBuilt a Node.js and Express.js backend to fetch the products data\nand image\nSKILLS\nTechnologies :- React.js, Node.js, Express.js, HTML, CSS,\nJavaScript\nFrontend\nHTML Instagram Clone\nCSS\nJavaScript This project is a simplified clone of Instagram's homepage,\nReact.js focusing on replicating the core layout and design elements\nBuilt with modern web development technologies, it showcases\nBackend how to create a visually appealing and responsive user interface\nNode.js Technologies :- React.js, Node.js, Express.js, HTML, CSS,\nExpress.js JavaScript\nDatabases\nFaceBook Clone\nSQL\nReplicated Instagram's core homepage layout and features for a\nMongoDB\nvisually appealing UI\nOther Tools\nImplemented responsive design principles to ensure cross-\nGit device compatibility\nPostman Technologies :-React.js , Node.js , Express.js Html,Css , Javascrip\nSoft Skills\nAdidas Homepage Clone\nTime Management\nExcellent Teamwork Developed a pixel-perfect replica of Adidas India's homepage\nProblem Solving Ability for design practice\nTechnologies :- HTML, CSS, JavaScript\nCERTIFICATIONS\nZomato Clone\nBuilt a visually accurate clone of Zomato India's homepage with\nReact.js (Basic) - HackerRank\na focus on UI/UX\nNode.js (Basic) - HackerRank\nTechnologies :- Html,Css , Javascript\nJavaScript (Basic) - HackerRank"}
