chnical challenges, collaborating\nwith cross-functional teams, and continuously learning to implement\nhttps://github.com/vaibhav2002\nmodern technologies for creating scalable and efficient solutions .\ndesale\nhttps://www.linkedin.com/in/vai\nbhav-desale/\nEDUCATION\nPROJECT’S\n2020 - 2024\nDBATU UNIVERSITY BIKERENT\nB.Tech in Computer Science\nDisplays a list of available bikes with details like images, type (e.g.,\nS.S.V.P.S College of Engineering\nroad, mountain, electric), pricing, and availability.\nEnsures the website looks great and works seamlessly across all\nSKILLS devices\nTechnologies :- react , javascript , node , HTML & CSS\nFlexibility\nAdaptability MAHASAFAR\nProblem Solving\nDiscover Maharashtra's rich heritage and natural wonders with\nTECHNICALSKILLS Mahasafar Explore majestic temples, ancient forts, serene caves,\nand scenic dams. Plan your journey with ease—book flights, rent\nFrontend Database rooms, villas, bikes, and cars, all in one place!\nHTML MongoDB Technologies :- React , Javascript , Node , HTML , CSS , MongoDB\nCSS SQL\nJavaScript WORKING\nLanguage\nReact.JS\nPython\nworking as a Backend Developer at AdeptAIPro company.\nBackend C\ndeveloped a searching algorithm using Python language,\nNode.js\nin which, working on semantic search and have used models.\nExpress.js\nbasic knowledge of AI/ML and I am learning it.\nTOOLS Technologies :- Python\nVisual Studio\nGit CERTIFICATE\nPostman\nReact.js (Basic) - HackerRank\nLANGUAGES\nNode.js (Basic) - HackerRank\nMarathi JavaScript (Basic) - HackerRank\nHindi\nEnglish"}
